-- Argentine President Changes Cabinet: Spokesman Scoccimarro
-- B y   P a b l o   G o n z a l e z
-- 2013-05-30T23:42:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-30/argentine-president-changes-cabinet-spokesman-scoccimarro.html
Agustin Rossi will be appointed as
Defense Minister; Arturo Puricelli will become Security
Minister, President Cristina Fernandez de Kirchner’s spokesman
Alfredo Scoccimarro said in televised statement from the
presidential house know as “pink house.”  * Nilda Garre to resign as Security Minister, will be appointed
as Ambassador to the Washington-based Organization of American
States (OAS): Scoccimarro  NOTE: Rossi was speaker of the house, Puriccelli was Defense
Minister.  To contact the reporter on this story:
